    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――時空の狭間が閉じるまであと9時間",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—9 Hours Until the Space-Time Rift Closes",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_watch-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "『モーター』が手に入りましたわ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve obtained the “Motor”~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.1333333452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "これで壊れてる所は、もうなさそうですわね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It looks like there’s nothing broken anymore!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.9666666786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 9.8559183875
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "後は燃料とかかな？　ここまで順調だね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe all that’s left is fuel? We’ve come this far without a hitch!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.8559183875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "この調子で、次の謎を探すぞ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s keep this momentum and find the next riddle~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4559183875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "よし、残るはあと『エネルギー』だけだ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All right‚ the only thing left is “Energy”!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.3625838715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "次のヒントは……あれ？　このペン書けないぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The next hint is… huh? This pen won’t write?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.8727131953,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_write-01.m4a",
          "delay": 49.87185879999956
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_write-01.m4a",
          "delay": 49.87185879999956
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ゲーシゲシゲシ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Geee-shi geshi geshi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.4304065504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "またかかったゲシな、{user}！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You fell for it again‚ {user}‚ geshi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.190407733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "ゴドノ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Godono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "フフ……聞いて驚かないでおくれ。実は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu… don’t be too shocked when you hear this. In fact…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.4637414096,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "ゴドノ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Godono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロ中のボールペンのキャップを外しておいたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I removed the caps from every ballpoint pen in Hoshimi Pro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.2232652783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なっ……！　そんなの、インクがカピカピになって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wha—!? Then the ink will dry out",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.1304101108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "使えなくなるじゃないか！　どうしてそんなことを！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and they’ll become unusable! Why would you do that!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.7225870887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "ズミレ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "自分が一番心当たりあるんとちゃいますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ain’t you the one who should know best why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.721112867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "ズミレ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "あんちゃん……さっきから怪しい行動してるやろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Bro… you’ve been acting suspicious this whole time‚ haven’t ya?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.3477791904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "ビボ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Bibo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "実はさ～さっきこっそりそいつのポッケ縫い付けて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ like‚ I secretly stitched his pocket shut earlier",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.3877774992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "ビボ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Bibo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "開かないようにしてたら、偶然聞いちゃったんだけど～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so it wouldn’t open~‚ and I just happened to overhear~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.0811125237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "ビボ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Bibo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "こいつ、さくら達と通信してたんだよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He was communicating with Sakura and the others!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4544441658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "ビボ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Bibo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "マシンがどうとか……マジありえなくない！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something about a machine… like‚ seriously‚ isn’t that insane!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.6144458571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なっ！　勝手にポケットにイタズラしてたのか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What!? You messed with my pocket without permission!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.2877815682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "くっ……卑怯な！　小さいから気付けないじゃないか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… that’s dirty! You’re so small I couldn’t even notice!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.0892537553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "ゴドノ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Godono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "フフ……だが、マシンのことを知っているのは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu… but only we should know about the machine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.867282466,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "ゴドノ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Godono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "私達だけ……この中に裏切り者がいるってことになるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Which means there must be a traitor among us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.0565986116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "ズズ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zuzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ユルセナイ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unforgivable…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.2672829746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "ズズ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zuzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ウラギリモノ、ツブス……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Traitor… crush…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.4000000119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ガナ！　お前、ミボとブランに会いたくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gana! You were crying because you wanted to see Mibo and Bran‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.0006152907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "泣いていたゲシな！？　怪しいゲシ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "weren’t you‚ geshi!? Suspicious‚ geshi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.6272805968,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "ガナ",
      "speakerNameEn": "gana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ひ、ひぃっ！　ミボちゃんとブランちゃんに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "E-eek! It’s true I want to see Mibo-chan and Bran-chan‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.4672773797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "ガナ",
      "speakerNameEn": "gana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "会いたいのは本当だけど、私何もしてませんよぉ～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but I didn’t do anything~!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.5606139301,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うるさいゲシ！　ガナはてるてる坊主の刑にするゲシ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Quiet‚ geshi! Gana‚ you’re sentenced to the “teru-teru bozu” punishment‚ geshi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.5339476069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "早くこっちに来るゲシ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Get over here‚ geshi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.3939472634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "バルゴ！　また怪しい動きが出来ないように",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Barugo! Make sure he can’t make any suspicious moves again—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.333943538,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "ポケットで見張っておくゲシ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "keep watch from inside the pocket‚ geshi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.0606139301,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（くそ……バルゴに見張られていて、うかつに動けない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Damn… with Barugo watching me‚ I can’t move carelessly.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.00061936,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（時空の狭間はどんどん閉じていくし、どうすれば……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（And the rift is closing more and more… what should I do…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.4559199134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "バルゴ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Barugo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "見張りになれて好都合YOYO！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being the lookout works out perfectly‚ YO YO!",
        "id": ""
      },
